Sudoku.Input

Class ReadFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Sudoku.Input.ReadFile

  • public class ReadFile
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that reads in a sudoku board to the a data structure It reads in the file to the 2D array and then assigns the value of the filereader to the array element It then shows the array at the end.
    Since:
    1.0 Initial development.
    Author:
    Ryan Gouldsmith
